<plot>The enigmatic Anto returns to Dublin for a wake and recalls a game he played as a child. As a young boy, Anto enjoyed playing the rope trick game with his friends - pretending to pull an invisible rope across the road and making oncoming cars stop suddenly. But, one day, a car didn't stop and swerved off the road and over a cliff.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?587752</url></doc>
